This is a computing paradigm that operates through co-presence
and topology instead of arithmetic. tick() propagates — it does
not calculate. Computation emerges from collision, not instruction.

This is not a toy. It is proven (436 tests, Lean4 formal proofs,
GPU substrate verified) and it works on real hardware.

Use it to learn. Use it to research. Use it to understand.
Do not use it to profit. Do not be reckless with it.

